    question: "What areas of Sylvan Park do you serve?",
    answer: "We serve all of Sylvan Park and surrounding areas including homes along Murphy Road, 51st Avenue, Charlotte Pike, and throughout the historic Sylvan Park neighborhood. From beautifully restored 1920s bungalows to modern new construction, we bring quality cleaning services to every Sylvan Park residence."
  },
  {
    question: "Do you have experience with Sylvan Park's historic bungalows?",
    answer: "Absolutely! Sylvan Park is renowned for its charming 1920s Craftsman bungalows and cottages. We understand the care these homes require - from original hardwood floors and built-in cabinetry to vintage tile and period fixtures. We use appropriate techniques that respect and preserve historic features while achieving a thorough clean."
  },
  {
