          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
            The homes themselves tell a hundred years of architectural story. Original 1920s Craftsman bungalows feature deep porches, original hardwoods, built-in bookcases, and the solid construction of a more careful era. Many have been lovingly restored and updated, adding modern kitchens and bathrooms while preserving period character. New construction fills occasional lots, designed to complement rather than overwhelm the neighborhood's scale.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">
            Whether you're in a perfectly preserved original bungalow or a newly renovated gem, your Sylvan Park home deserves cleaning services that understand its value. The Valley Clean Team appreciates what makes this neighborhood special and delivers the quality care your home deserves.
          </p>
        </div>
