          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#333333] mb-6">Sylvan Park Home Features:</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="check" class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" />
              <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>1,200-2,500 sq ft</strong> bungalows and cottages</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
